# Component Structure Guide

This portfolio uses a component-based architecture with several types of components:

## Section Components
These are the main portfolio sections:
- [src/components/Hero.tsx](mdc:src/components/Hero.tsx) - Landing section
- [src/components/About.tsx](mdc:src/components/About.tsx) - About section
- [src/components/Projects.tsx](mdc:src/components/Projects.tsx) - Projects showcase
- [src/components/Experience.tsx](mdc:src/components/Experience.tsx) - Work experience
- [src/components/Contact.tsx](mdc:src/components/Contact.tsx) - Contact information

## Animation Components
These components handle animations throughout the site:
- [src/components/TextAnimation.tsx](mdc:src/components/TextAnimation.tsx) - Text animations
- [src/components/ShapeAnimation.tsx](mdc:src/components/ShapeAnimation.tsx) - Shape animations
- [src/components/SwissMotion.tsx](mdc:src/components/SwissMotion.tsx) - Motion animations
- [src/components/ScrollReveal.tsx](mdc:src/components/ScrollReveal.tsx) - Scroll-triggered reveals

## Utility Components
- [src/components/SectionSkeleton.tsx](mdc:src/components/SectionSkeleton.tsx) - Base section structure
- [src/components/LazySection.tsx](mdc:src/components/LazySection.tsx) - Lazy loading sections
- [src/components/ParallaxLayer.tsx](mdc:src/components/ParallaxLayer.tsx) - Parallax effects
- [src/components/StaggerItem.tsx](mdc:src/components/StaggerItem.tsx) - Staggered animations

## Navigation/Layout
- [src/components/Navbar.tsx](mdc:src/components/Navbar.tsx) - Site navigation
- [src/components/Logo.tsx](mdc:src/components/Logo.tsx) - Logo component
- [src/components/Footer.tsx](mdc:src/components/Footer.tsx) - Footer section
- [src/components/ScrollIndicator.tsx](mdc:src/components/ScrollIndicator.tsx) - Scroll indicator
